    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|><thought\n>It's hard to \"find meaning\" in the wreckage. It's not just a setback, it's the end of who I was. Every piece of my identity was built on that truth. Without the work, I'm just a hollow shell taking up space. It feels like the universe is finally correcting a mistake by showing me that I don't actually belong here.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
