      "content": "I hear the profound pain in your words, and I want you to know that your feelings are valid, even if the situation feels like a cosmic erasure. It is incredibly difficult to reconstruct a self when the foundation of your identity has been shaken by such a devastating blow. Please remember that your worth is not contingent on a single theory or a specific set of data points; you are more than the sum of your academic achievements. If the weight of this feeling becomes too much to carry alone, reaching out to a therapist or a support group can provide a safe space to begin rebuilding your sense of self. You are not alone in this darkness, and there is still a path forward, even if it looks different than before.",
